Description:
This altar is crowded, but among all the pilgrims, a group of warriors catches your attention as they use a sacred candle to ritually burn their bodies, seeking the blessing of the Great Bird’s strength.

The altar features a golden statue of the Great Bird, surrounded by numerous offerings and gifts from the pilgrims. A young snake, nestled among the gifts, watches everyone in the chamber with curious eyes, though by its expression, you’d guess it’s bored.

The guards observe the rites with interest.
DescriptionAction: Will you do something in this place?
